title: #92Noon Live From Lynx Training Camp
description: Broadcasting live from Mayo Clinic Square where Lynx training camp is going on, we're celebrating all the incredible women in Minnesota sports: Simone Augustus, Lynx Coach Cheryl Reeve, Fox Sports' Kyndra de St. Aubin, Fox 9's Dawn Mitchell and Marney Gellnar.
